\cos 60^\circ = \frac {x^2 + y^2 - w^2}{2xy} = \frac 1 2
w=DB=\frac {3 \sqrt 3}{2}
\cos \angle ADB=\frac{y^2+w^2-x^2}{2yw}=\frac{(\frac 3 2)^2+(\frac {3 \sqrt 3}{2})^2-3^2}{2 \frac 3 2\frac {3 \sqrt 3}{2}}=0
